{"tid":740882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士疑紅隧口飛站 乘客不滿怒踢車門","createTime":"2018-07-13T08:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T12:08:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"151fe1613430039d01a0766f9bc525ab56f26a2c","tid":740882,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"巴士司機與乘客不時產生磨擦，一輛由寶馬山開往九龍灣的108過海九巴，途經紅隧口巴士站時，疑有乘客不滿車長懷疑飛站，令大批乘客未能在紅磡站上車或下車，引起乘客不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊事發經過的乘客於Facebook專頁「巴打絲打」發文，指當時巴士已駛至下一站，多名乘客落車圍着巴士鼓譟，有人指責車長不在紅隧口停車，飛站至山谷道，其中一名男乘客情緒激動，邊用粗口責怪車長，邊起腳怒踢車門。而涉事車長則一直坐在駕駛座上，期間亦有乘客向他查問如何返回紅磡站。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民睇片後質疑「當時有無人襟鐘」認為車長不會故意飛站，亦有人認為即使車長做錯，乘客亦不應踢門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180713/_2018071315042898869.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180713%2F_2018071315042898869.jpg&h=6313ac5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1264983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1264983%2F&d=RMO9wrFjHlowV%2BoHQbAkzk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4e92fd38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1264983%2F&h=f909bdc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1264983/</a>"},{"pid":"c0aee1d28ebc0181eab65d0a7b751970060ef687","tid":740882,"uid":15,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"再嘈就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8053cd8ba8905db468dd328cb89192afeac5d3cb","tid":740882,"uid":44333,"like":27,"dislike":37,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:33:32.000Z","msg":"當個社會變成咁樣 就算幾有錢都無用"},{"pid":"b55a8fb2cdf591b00b4fac51846cc54be84df6f4","tid":740882,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cb839d9a04fcffdbcdd860db7416564a7fd33e","tid":740882,"uid":108347,"like":115,"dislike":2,"score":113,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"試過好幾次係d多人落的站個撚個諗住實有人㯲點知就係冇人㯲，真係見親都笑<br />\n<br />\n呢單都好有可能係，司機做咩要特登唔停先，自己7完屌司機真係好撚羞家"},{"pid":"9d596a2e7ee99df291d82a4e95df2c10843ef330","tid":740882,"uid":51620,"like":55,"dislike":6,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"34cb839d9a04fcffdbcdd860db7416564a7fd33e","tid":740882,"uid":108347,"like":115,"dislike":2,"score":113,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"試過好幾次係d多人落的站個撚個諗住實有人㯲點知就係冇人㯲，真係見親都笑<br />\n<br />\n呢單都好有可能係，司機做咩要特登唔停先，自己7完屌司機真係好撚羞家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"除左唔禁鐘落車 仲有d人唔揮手 自以為司機識讀心術知佢要上車<br />\n<br />\n架車走左就屌屌聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d17e1b4b5e77142bd8a127735cd2ce2cdc66abc","tid":740882,"uid":70888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:04:42.000Z","msg":"試過連續幾次同一個車長禁鐘唔開車門，每次都要大大聲講有落，依家佢唔敢再飛站"},{"pid":"23933641a34421941727b74f67717164432cda99","tid":740882,"uid":78399,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"d人成日以為某d站實有人落<br />\n之後個個都唔㩒鐘"},{"pid":"09e150f1285094208ff639e863cd877d077c656d","tid":740882,"uid":39628,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"23933641a34421941727b74f67717164432cda99","tid":740882,"uid":78399,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"d人成日以為某d站實有人落<br />\n之後個個都唔㩒鐘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"真係抵死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c01e42d20cc7786c96afa8e4c99d7bd1ee05097","tid":740882,"uid":31227,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:26:43.000Z","msg"